import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-manage-faq', templateUrl: './manage-faq.page.html', styleUrls: ['./manage-faq.page.scss'], }) export class ManageFAQPage implements OnInit { constructor(private router:Router) { } ngOnInit() { } goBack(){ this.router.navigate(['medical-faq']); } } Medical FAQs
Patient Assessment What is the first responsibility of the EMT-B on the scene of an emergency before starting to assess the patient? SCENE SIZE-UP
1. Dispatch information
2. Body Substance Isolation
3. Scene Safety/Scene hazards
4. Mechanism of injury/ Nature of illness
5. Number of patients
6. Additional resources needed
7. C-Spine Immobilization
